|    rule id    |               V554              |
+---------------+---------------------------------+
|   rule name   |    IncorrectUseOfSmartPointer   |
+---------------+---------------------------------+
| rule category |         UnderlyingError         |
+---------------+---------------------------------+
|   rule check  |        smart指针使用错误        |
+---------------+---------------------------------+
|    message    | Incorrect use of smart pointer. |
+---------------+---------------------------------+

代码示例总结：
+----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
